---
---
<style>
  .bio-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .bio-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px; }
    .bio-headshot { max-height: none; }
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .bio-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 420px; }
  }
  .bio-headshot { max-height: 380px; }
</style>
<section class="sr bg-white">
  <div class="bio-grid max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-14 py-12 md:py-16 grid gap-6 md:gap-10 items-center">
    <!-- Left: text -->
    <div>
      <p class="tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-7" style="font-size:17px; color:var(--color-amber);">The Work</p>
      <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.85] mb-5" style="color:#444;">
        James Tannahill works at the intersection of complex systems: biological, financial, digital, operational.
        His discipline is engineering resilience - structures built to absorb pressure and compound advantage.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.85] mb-5" style="color:#444;">
        He operates across healthcare, industrials, technology, and finance. His background spans biochemistry,
        biotechnology, equity research, strategic finance, and private equity operations.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.85]" style="color:#444;">
        MBA from Cornell's Johnson School of Management. He leads Plocamium Holdings,
        runs 1nessAgency and RDLB, and builds AI-native software.
      </p>
    </div>
    <!-- Right: headshot -->
    <div class="relative">
      <picture>
        <source srcset="/headshot.webp" type="image/webp" />
        <img
          src="/headshot.jpg"
          alt="James Tannahill"
          width="840"
          height="1120"
          class="w-full block"
          class="bio-headshot w-full block"
          style="aspect-ratio:3/4; object-fit:cover; object-position:center top;"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </picture>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-[3px]" style="background:var(--color-amber);"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
